<doc id="1189142" wikidata="Q592273" url="?curid=1189142" title="Bostrichiformia">
<text>Bostrichiformia is an infraorder of polyphagan beetles.

It contains two superfamilies, Derodontoidea and Bostrichoidea, which includes the Dermestidae, Ptinidae, Bostrichidae and others.

