* 1903–1925: &quot;Museum of Fine Arts Bulletin&quot;
* 1926–1965: &quot;Bulletin of the Museum of Fine Arts&quot;
* 1966–1977: &quot;Boston Museum Bulletin&quot;
* 1978–1980: &quot;MFA Bulletin&quot;
* 1981–1983: &quot;M Bulletin (Museum of Fine Arts, Boston)&quot;

